                Buccioni <lb n="2"/>Ressima<lb break="no" n="3"/>ri <expan><abbr>fil</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> et <lb n="4"/>Taparuni <lb n="5"/>Senici <expan><abbr>fil</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost">c</supplied>on</abbr><ex>iugi</ex></expan> et <lb n="7"/>Vindoni <lb n="8"/>f<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>il</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan></supplied> <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XXXX
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Ligaturen: Z. 1 und 4: NI; I-longa: Z. 1, 3, 4 und 5. Die Buchstaben T ragen über die Zeilenhöhe hinaus. Im Giebel ein Medusenhaupt, in den Zwickeln Delphine. Material: grauer Marmor. (B): CIL III: Z. 5: Senicii f(i)l(iae).</p>
            </div>
